Can you please keep...

277
00:25:16,886 --> 00:25:18,521
my memory for me?

278
00:25:37,073 --> 00:25:38,073
Let's go.

279
00:25:38,675 --> 00:25:39,675
We should get back.

280
00:25:53,790 --> 00:25:55,125
How are things at home?

281
00:25:56,393 --> 00:25:59,696
Uncle's back home, the doctor gave him some medication.

282
00:26:01,131 --> 00:26:04,134
They said that there's no symptoms to be worried about.

283
00:26:04,434 --> 00:26:05,669
No need to be stressed.

284
00:26:05,935 --> 00:26:07,871
It's a relief that there's nothing big.

285
00:26:08,471 --> 00:26:11,351
These days, my family's been experiencing a lot of stressful situations.

286
00:26:11,508 --> 00:26:15,078
Our luck's been down, probably because of my quarter life crisis?

287
00:26:16,312 --> 00:26:18,815
That's got nothing to do with this, it's a matter of health.

288
00:26:20,550 --> 00:26:24,254
But I don't want you to experience any bad things like this, Tao Sor.

289
00:26:24,454 --> 00:26:25,454
I think...

290
00:26:26,122 --> 00:26:27,791
being able to meet you...

291
00:26:28,425 --> 00:26:30,326
is one of the best things to happen to me.

292
00:26:37,434 --> 00:26:38,434
And...

293
00:26:38,802 --> 00:26:41,805
how would you know if you've ever experienced anything good before?

294
00:26:42,839 --> 00:26:43,839
Today...

295
00:26:44,240 --> 00:26:45,842
I drew so many pictues of us.

296
00:26:48,445 --> 00:26:49,546
You know something?

297
00:26:51,047 --> 00:26:53,650
You're very talented in drawing.

298
00:26:57,987 --> 00:27:01,958
Some day, I'll take you to my studio.

299
00:27:02,358 --> 00:27:03,626
If I remember to.

300
00:27:04,527 --> 00:27:07,063
Deal! Because if you don't remember,

301
00:27:07,664 --> 00:27:09,332
I'll go to your place myself!

302
00:27:13,703 --> 00:27:14,703
Tao Sor!

303
00:27:17,173 --> 00:27:18,173
Tao Sor!

304
00:27:21,044 --> 00:27:22,044
Yes?

305
00:27:23,713 --> 00:27:26,716
Nothing. I think you should get some rest.

306
00:27:35,992 --> 00:27:38,728
Kim. When I wake up,

307
00:27:39,729 --> 00:27:41,231
will I remember you?

308
00:27:42,165 --> 00:27:45,001
I told you already, you don't have to worry about that.

309
00:27:45,568 --> 00:27:47,070
Even if you won't remember,

310
00:27:47,270 --> 00:27:51,407
I'll be here, re-introducing myself each time.

311
00:27:53,209 --> 00:27:56,212
Trust me, okay? Get some rest.

312
00:28:08,224 --> 00:28:10,226
I love you, Kim.

313
00:28:21,938 --> 00:28:22,938
And what is this?

314
00:28:23,540 --> 00:28:24,540
You got a tattoo?

315
00:28:25,909 --> 00:28:27,477
Can I just have my own life?

316
00:28:28,545 --> 00:28:30,580
The reason I have to know everything about you,

317
00:28:31,114 --> 00:28:34,751
is so I can tell you what happened the day before each time you wake up!

318
00:28:36,419 --> 00:28:37,730
But did he choose to go with you?

319
00:28:37,754 --> 00:28:39,189
Or did you decide for him?

320
00:28:41,591 --> 00:28:42,892
Did he hurt me?

321
00:28:45,662 --> 00:28:47,497
He made your life chaotic.

322
00:28:49,666 --> 00:28:51,201
You little...
- I love Tao Sor!

323
00:29:37,947 --> 00:29:41,184
You are Tao Sor, you love Kim.

324
00:29:41,618 --> 00:29:44,821
He is your boyfriend, don't tell anyone about this.

325
00:30:05,742 --> 00:30:06,742
Tao Sor!

326
00:30:08,511 --> 00:30:09,913
Tao Sor! Why'd you lock your door?

327
00:30:13,383 --> 00:30:14,383
Tao Sor!

328
00:30:15,051 --> 00:30:16,051
Yes?

329
00:30:18,221 --> 00:30:19,222
Why'd you lock the door?

330
00:30:21,591 --> 00:30:22,591
Oh...

331
00:30:23,426 --> 00:30:24,426
I don't know why.

332
00:30:28,598 --> 00:30:31,034
I'm Talay, I'm your older brother.

333
00:30:32,035 --> 00:30:33,069
Oh..

334
00:30:33,670 --> 00:30:34,670
Remember?

335
00:30:38,107 --> 00:30:39,208
I can't...

336
00:30:53,056 --> 00:30:56,893
Dad. Eat your food so you can take your medicine.
- Hm? Okay.

337
00:30:59,963 --> 00:31:02,883
Did you practice your breathing like the doctor told you to this morning?

338
00:31:03,399 --> 00:31:06,936
I'm already breathing. If I wasn't, I'd be dead, right?

339
00:31:07,737 --> 00:31:11,274
I know, but I meant practicing breathing like the doctor prescribed.

340
00:31:11,441 --> 00:31:13,376
So you won't get stressed.

341
00:31:17,613 --> 00:31:19,082
We're having porridge today?

342
00:31:20,149 --> 00:31:22,618
In that case, I'll go eat something at the university.

343
00:31:22,752 --> 00:31:25,355
I woke up late. Finished work up a bit late.

344
00:31:26,489 --> 00:31:29,192
I'm off, Sang! See you, Dad.

345
00:31:35,798 --> 00:31:37,033
Everyone.

346
00:31:37,433 --> 00:31:39,569
Shall we get some cake today?

347
00:31:41,070 --> 00:31:42,070
Cake?

348
00:31:42,271 --> 00:31:44,774
You know, the chocolate cake from the regular spot.

349
00:31:49,312 --> 00:31:51,814
I won't have any, I'm cutting down on fat.

350
00:31:53,516 --> 00:31:56,652
The doctor's making me watch my diet, some other time then.

351
00:32:35,958 --> 00:32:38,094
Hello, I'm picking up the cake I ordered.
- Hello.

352
00:32:38,294 --> 00:32:40,797
The name is Kim.
- Okay, please sit and wait for a moment.

353
00:32:48,171 --> 00:32:50,506
The birthday cake for Tao Sor's ready!

354
00:32:57,547 --> 00:32:58,815
Thank you.

355
00:33:01,150 --> 00:33:02,150
Tao Sor!

356
00:33:07,256 --> 00:33:09,425
It's your birthday?

357
00:33:11,260 --> 00:33:13,695
No. A client is having a birthday today,

358
00:33:13,696 --> 00:33:15,598
so I came to get the cake they ordered.

359
00:33:15,832 --> 00:33:18,067
By the way, do we know each other?

360
00:33:19,535 --> 00:33:20,870
We know each other very well.

361
00:33:21,471 --> 00:33:22,471
I'm Kim.

362
00:33:39,422 --> 00:33:41,757
I'm sorry. I have to get going.

363
00:33:42,191 --> 00:33:44,627
But I really wanna know...

364
00:33:46,229 --> 00:33:47,597
who you are.

365
00:33:49,298 --> 00:33:50,633
Can we see each other again?

366
00:33:51,234 --> 00:33:52,234
Then...

367
00:33:53,035 --> 00:33:55,138
we'll meet at the Siam Sea port.

368
00:33:55,972 --> 00:33:56,972
I'll be waiting.

369
00:33:58,341 --> 00:33:59,341
Can do.

370
00:34:06,883 --> 00:34:09,585
The birthday cake for Kim is ready!

371
00:34:37,780 --> 00:34:39,382
Happy Birthday, Kim!

372
00:34:43,352 --> 00:34:46,355
Actually, today's not really my birthday.

373
00:34:47,089 --> 00:34:48,858
Oh, then who's is it?

374
00:34:52,695 --> 00:34:53,695
My older brother.

375
00:34:55,631 --> 00:34:56,631
Have a seat.

376
00:35:04,740 --> 00:35:06,108
And...

377
00:35:07,076 --> 00:35:08,711
your brother's not celebrating with you?

378
00:35:09,145 --> 00:35:10,145
He's...

379
00:35:11,614 --> 00:35:12,949
not here anymore.

380
00:35:14,517 --> 00:35:16,385
We probably can't celebrate anymore.

381
00:35:18,788 --> 00:35:22,158
I just wanted to think about him today.

382
00:35:22,558 --> 00:35:23,559
That's all.

383
00:35:24,393 --> 00:35:25,628
If I heard that,

384
00:35:25,995 --> 00:35:27,296
as a brother, I'd be very happy.

385
00:35:27,730 --> 00:35:29,865
That someone remembers him.

386
00:35:30,433 --> 00:35:31,601
But me?

387
00:35:33,102 --> 00:35:35,104
I can't even remember my own birthday.

388
00:35:38,274 --> 00:35:39,274
How bout this?

389
00:35:39,475 --> 00:35:42,979
Why don't we celebrate your birthday, today.

390
00:35:43,980 --> 00:35:47,450
It'll just be us two, so we can take the boat out,

391
00:35:48,618 --> 00:35:49,986
and go somewhere we can be alone.

392
00:36:04,100 --> 00:36:05,434
Don't be scared.

393
00:36:07,303 --> 00:36:09,071
I'll be right beside you.

394
00:36:14,510 --> 00:36:17,513
Happy Birthday,

395
00:36:17,713 --> 00:36:20,716
to you...

396
00:36:24,320 --> 00:36:25,320
So,

397
00:36:27,156 --> 00:36:28,691
let's make a wish together.

398
00:36:46,142 --> 00:36:49,145
You're... my boyfriend?

399
00:36:53,349 --> 00:36:54,349
Do...

400
00:36:55,217 --> 00:36:56,252
you remember me?

401
00:36:58,321 --> 00:36:59,822
Oh, that's not it.

402
00:37:00,222 --> 00:37:04,093
This morning I saw a note, and these drawings.

403
00:37:34,690 --> 00:37:35,690
Do...

404
00:37:36,058 --> 00:37:37,693
you know the person in this drawing?

405
00:37:38,027 --> 00:37:39,027
Oh...

406
00:37:39,562 --> 00:37:41,197
No, I don't. I just...

407
00:37:41,897 --> 00:37:44,900
dreamt that this boy saved another boy from drowning.

408
00:37:47,937 --> 00:37:50,940
So I just drew him.

409
00:37:58,914 --> 00:37:59,914
Are you okay?

410
00:38:00,583 --> 00:38:03,853
I think I'll tell the captain to go back.

411
00:38:05,354 --> 00:38:06,354
You wait here.

412
00:38:09,158 --> 00:38:10,359
Yes, that's right.

413
00:38:10,659 --> 00:38:12,461
This point, please fix it for me.

414
00:38:13,596 --> 00:38:14,930
Okay...

415
00:38:15,664 --> 00:38:17,533
Can do, send the file over to me too.

416
00:38:17,900 --> 00:38:18,900
Okay.

417
00:38:30,279 --> 00:38:31,279
Hey.

418
00:38:33,315 --> 00:38:34,350
What are you doing here?

419
00:38:35,351 --> 00:38:36,352
Where's my brother?

420
00:38:37,953 --> 00:38:39,054
How would I know that?

421
00:38:39,388 --> 00:38:41,257
Your brother took mine here, right?

422
00:38:43,392 --> 00:38:44,460
You mean Siw?

423
00:38:44,960 --> 00:38:45,995
No.

424
00:38:46,495 --> 00:38:49,064
Is there a problem? What did Kim do?

425
00:38:50,065 --> 00:38:51,934
I just want to know where my brother is.

426
00:38:52,868 --> 00:38:54,103
My brother is sick.

427
00:38:54,270 --> 00:38:55,971
If anything happens to him,

428
00:38:56,372 --> 00:38:58,674
I won't be doing any more business with Siam Sea.

429
00:38:58,741 --> 00:39:00,309
Sang, go check.

430
00:39:00,876 --> 00:39:01,876
Okay, Dad.

431
00:39:24,133 --> 00:39:25,134
It's true, Dad.

432
00:39:25,601 --> 00:39:26,841
There's one ship out right now.

433
00:39:27,102 --> 00:39:28,502
How are you taking care of things?!

434
00:39:28,637 --> 00:39:30,906
Well Dad, it's...

435
00:39:31,874 --> 00:39:33,709
it's the one with the issues.

436
00:39:34,777 --> 00:39:35,777
What did you say?

437
00:39:36,345 --> 00:39:37,780
A faulty ship?

438
00:39:38,314 --> 00:39:40,182
And you just let my brother go?!

439
00:39:42,718 --> 00:39:44,153
I just found out as well, like you!

440
00:39:46,355 --> 00:39:47,556
Let's do this, Dad.

441
00:39:47,756 --> 00:39:49,568
I'll hurry and get some people to go look for them.

442
00:39:49,592 --> 00:39:50,059
Get to it!

443
00:39:50,359 --> 00:39:51,359
I'll go too!

444
00:41:27,389 --> 00:41:28,390
Are you okay?

445
00:41:29,091 --> 00:41:30,593
I'm okay, bro.

446
00:41:30,859 --> 00:41:32,962
You don't have to go, I'll take the clients myself.

447
00:41:34,396 --> 00:41:35,664
But this job...
- Just go home.

448
00:41:36,065 --> 00:41:37,065
It's okay.

449
00:41:37,533 --> 00:41:38,634
You've been tired all day.

450
00:41:39,101 --> 00:41:41,270
If I get any tips, I'll share them with you.

451
00:41:43,706 --> 00:41:46,342
Okay, bro. Thanks alot.

452
00:41:59,521 --> 00:42:01,023
Take care of yourself.

453
00:42:01,991 --> 00:42:04,059
Hurry back!

454
00:42:35,624 --> 00:42:36,624
Tao Sor,

455
00:42:37,493 --> 00:42:38,994
You can hear me, right?

456
00:42:41,430 --> 00:42:43,032
Forget everything.

457
00:42:44,299 --> 00:42:46,468
And come back to being my brother, okay?

458
00:42:46,669 --> 00:42:48,370
If you really feel bad,

459
00:42:48,871 --> 00:42:50,105
then I beg you.

460
00:42:50,839 --> 00:42:53,409
Quit messing with that family's son!

461
00:42:53,642 --> 00:42:57,546
Any drawings that aren't my parents or me, get rid of all of them.

462
00:42:57,880 --> 00:43:00,315
Tao Sor has no need for these memories.

463
00:43:00,816 --> 00:43:03,485
We must clear out everything that would destroy his life.

